	<article id="post-3295" class="post-3295 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-accountability category-big-brother category-civil-liberties category-current-affairs category-democracy category-intelligence category-law category-libya category-manning category-mi5 category-mi6 category-national-security category-nsa category-police category-privacy-2 category-snowden category-spies category-surveillance category-syria category-talks-2 category-torture category-war-2 category-whistleblowers category-wikileaks tag-berlin tag-intelligence-2 tag-international-day-of-privacy tag-law-2 tag-manning tag-nsa tag-police-2 tag-privacy tag-snowden tag-spies-2 tag-surveillance-2 tag-syria tag-talk tag-whistleblowers-2 tag-wikileaks">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/09/international-day-privacy-berlin-demo.html" title="Permalink to International Day of Privacy, Berlin Demo" rel="bookmark">International Day of Privacy, Berlin Demo</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/09/international-day-privacy-berlin-demo.html" title="13:00" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-09-18T13:00:34+00:00" pubdate>September 18, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/09/international-day-privacy-berlin-demo.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>The <a href="http://demonstrare.de/demonstrare/stopwatchingus-international-day-of-privacy-idp-31-08-2013">Inter­na­tional Day of Pri­vacy</a> was cel­eb­rated glob­ally on 31 August, with the cases of Chelsea Man­ning and Edward Snowden bring­ing extra energy and res­on­ance to the subject.</p>
<p>I was invited take part in a demon­stra­tion in Ber­lin, cul­min­at­ing with a talk at the hugely sym­bolic <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brandenburg_Gate">Branden­burg Gate</a>. Here’s the talk:<br />
<iframe width="420" height="315" src="//www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/VrYTjvMJtyM" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
