				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/bani-walid" rel="tag">Bani Walid</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/gaddafi" rel="tag">Gaddafi</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/libya" rel="tag">Libya</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/machon" rel="tag">Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/mi6" rel="tag">MI6</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/nato" rel="tag">NATO</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/rttv" rel="tag">RTTV</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/war" rel="tag">war</a>			</span>
						
