							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/belhaj" rel="tag">Belhaj</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/iraq" rel="tag">Iraq</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/jack-straw" rel="tag">Jack Straw</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/law-2" rel="tag">law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/libya" rel="tag">Libya</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/osa" rel="tag">OSA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/pacificism" rel="tag">pacificism</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/tony-blair" rel="tag">Tony Blair</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/war" rel="tag">war</a>			</span>
						
