							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/david-shayler" rel="tag">David Shayler</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/dr-eamonn-oneill" rel="tag">Dr Eamonn O'Neill</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/esquire" rel="tag">Esquire</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblower" rel="tag">whistleblower</a>			</span>
						
