				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/belhaj" rel="tag">Belhaj</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/gaddafi" rel="tag">Gaddafi</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/islamist" rel="tag">Islamist</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/jibril" rel="tag">Jibril</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/libya" rel="tag">Libya</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/lifg" rel="tag">LIFG</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/mi6" rel="tag">MI6</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/torture-2" rel="tag">torture</a>			</span>
						
